---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="The Stability Footwear Master Matrix | Practical Podiatrist">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-slate-300 relative z-10">
    <header class="mb-12 border-b border-white/10 pb-8 text-center">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">Biomechanical Footwear Guide</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">The Stability Shoe Matrix</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Why letting "comfort be your only guide" is a dangerous retail deception trap for failing feet.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="space-y-8 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>True comfort requires structural stiffness that holds your foot in a neutral position.</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Maximum Control Tanks:</strong> Brooks Addiction, Brooks Beast, Brooks Ariel.</li>
        <li><strong>Premium Everyday Support:</strong> Hoka Arahi, Brooks Adrenaline, New Balance 860, Asics Gel-Kayano.</li>
        <li><strong>Reliable / Budget Stability:</strong> Asics GT-2000, Asics GT-1000, Mizuno Wave Inspire.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-red-400 font-bold">NEVER wear Altra or zero-drop minimalist models during an active injury cycle; they stretch the fascia to its absolute limit.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
